{"tid":2290933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「第二十九日」香港警察還不想破獲侮辱何俊堯法官既案件","createTime":"2020-11-18T11:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T04:51:25.000Z","uid":230104,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5f4e8a161f912d490a5cf2c98ee0738dd7c03f2","tid":2290933,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BCY4j2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BCY4j2.png&h=7597274b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周二（20日）晚上11時，5男乘坐白色凌志私家車到達九龍塘馬可尼道，其中4人落地，在私人住宅馬可尼大廈和康樂閣外抛雜物，同時在兩棟大廈外牆噴紅油，繁簡夾雜寫上「狗官何俊堯，警察拉人，狗官放人，目无法紀」、「差人拉人，9官放人，正X街」等大字。"},{"pid":"be4cf14849d8ebe102962c31550f7bdf8e15ded5","tid":2290933,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"之前係未能，而家好明顯係不願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171c27dc2d7cf60d8c25f5d311dc44ab2daf2967","tid":2290933,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1261bbc80cc96c7cb7e6de4a7bb2f8e0ffb7d5c5","tid":2290933,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"6e1e228ed2acd14f8a87fa69501409f6c35ef3ef","tid":2290933,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"藍屍殺人放火金腰帶"},{"pid":"77a81543f1dba16a5cbcba14e39115094988995c","tid":2290933,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889869921140a3919faf2505327c80df0f8a229f","tid":2290933,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">5男乘坐白色凌志私家車</span></span>"},{"pid":"93a09fdc29087d43db3b324ae2832d938194f804","tid":2290933,"uid":53498,"like"